```  

```  

## MCP File Service Syntax  

![Robodog MCP File Service](screenshot-mcp.png)  
```txt
/include all
/include file=*.md
/include pattern=*service*.js recursive
/include dir=src pattern=*.py recursive
```
*Globs: `*`, `?`, character classes. No full regex.*  

---

## MCP Server Startup  

```bash
python robodog.py --folders c:\projects\robodog\robodogcli --port 2500 --token testtoken --config config.yaml --model o4-mini
```  

---

## Supported File Formats  

- Text & Markdown: `.txt`, `.md`, `.markdown`  
- Code: `.js`, `.ts`, `.py`, `.java`, `.c`, `.cpp`, `.go`, `.rs`  
- Config/Data: `.yaml`, `.yml`, `.json`, `.xml`, `.csv`  
- PDF: `.pdf`  
- Images: `.png`, `.jpg`, `.jpeg`, `.gif`, `.bmp`, `.tiff`, `.pbm`, `.pgm`, `.ppm`  

---

## Command Reference  

Run `/help` in-app or see the list below:  

```
/help                    ‚Äî show help  
/model <name>            ‚Äî switch model  
/import                  ‚Äî import files  
/export <filename>       ‚Äî export snapshot  
/clear                   ‚Äî clear chat & knowledge  
/stash <name>            ‚Äî stash chat+knowledge  
/pop   <name>            ‚Äî retrieve stash  
/list                    ‚Äî list stashes  
/temperature <n>         ‚Äî set temperature (0‚Äì2)  
/max_tokens <n>          ‚Äî set max tokens  
/top_p <n>               ‚Äî set nucleus sampling  
/frequency_penalty <n>   ‚Äî set frequency penalty  
/presence_penalty <n>    ‚Äî set presence penalty  
/rest                    ‚Äî use REST completions  
/stream                  ‚Äî use streaming completions  
/include ‚Ä¶               ‚Äî include files via MCP  
/play <instructions>     ‚Äî run AI-driven Playwright tests against a website: parses your instructions into code, executes each step, and summarizes success/failure
```

*Also supports keyboard shortcuts:*  
- CTRL+SHIFT+UP to cycle stashes  
- CTRL+S to save a snapshot  

